This is a patch to add dxr3/hollywood+ support to xine.
It if doesn't apply cleanly you can checkout xine cvs from the date on the patch.
There also may be a more current version at http://www.kuroyi.net/xine

cvs -z3 -d:pserver:anonymous@cvs.xine.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/xine co xine
patch -p0 <xine_dxr3.patch
cd xine
./autogen.sh --enable-dxr3
make
make install
cd ..

You may want to read the Xine FAQ for info about CSS, etc.

Run it with:

xine_dxr3 -A dxr3
or
xine_dxr3 -A dxr3 -t pal
or
xine_dxr3 -S -A dxr3
or
xine_dxr3 -a1 -u0 -A dxr3
